Package it.polimi.ingsw.project.client.gui.listeners.market

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ArrowListener
    it is used when you want to insert a marble in the market
    CoinHandListener
    it is used to make you select a coin when you collected it in the market move
    DeselectButtonListener
    it is used to make you deselect the resources that you selected before during the market move
    DiscardButtonListener
    it is used to make you discard the resources that you selected during the market move
    InsertExtraDepositButtonListener
    it is used to insert the resources that you selected during the market move in the extradeposit
    InsertFirstShelfButtonListener
    it is used to insert the resources that you selected during the market move in the first shelf
    InsertSecondShelfButtonListener
    it is used to insert the resources that you selected during the market move in the second shelf
    InsertThirdShelfButtonListener
    it is used to insert the resources that you selected during the market move in the third shelf
    ServantHandListener
    it is used to make you select a servant when you collected it in the market move
    ShieldHandListener
    it is used to make you select a shield when you collected it in the market move
    StoneHandListener
    it is used to make you select a stone when you collected it in the market move
